WEBVTT

00:02.100 --> 00:03.294
PREVIOUSLY...

00:03.300 --> 00:05.359
STOP BY THE OFFICE,
AND WELL FINISH UP.

00:05.370 --> 00:07.691
IM REFERRING TO THE REWARD.
VERONICA AND I
HAD AN ARRANGEMENT.

00:07.700 --> 00:10.533
IM A MURDERER AND A RAPIST NOW.
I SLEPT WITH YOU!

00:10.540 --> 00:13.100
WHAT ABOUT THAT
IS SO WRONG?!
CAUSE YOURE MY SISTER!

00:13.110 --> 00:14.634
I KNOW
YOU WERE WITH ABEL KOONTZ

00:14.640 --> 00:17.006
AT THE TIME HE SUPPOSEDLY
MURDERED LILLY KANE.

00:17.010 --> 00:18.739
YOU THINK THEYRE SERIOUS?
IT WONT LAST LONG.

00:18.740 --> 00:21.243
MOMS IN REHAB. WHEN SHE GETS
CLEANED UP, SHES COMING HOME.

00:21.250 --> 00:23.241
THINK YOURE GONNA LAY A HAND
ON HER THE WAY YOU DID LILLY --

00:23.250 --> 00:25.684
DONT YOU EVEN SAY
HER NAME.

00:25.690 --> 00:27.214
YOU LEARNED THAT
FROM LILLY?

00:32.200 --> 00:35.454
NOW, LET ME MAKE SURE
IM HEARING THIS CORRECT LY.

00:35.460 --> 00:38.122
ABEL KOONTZ COULDNT HAVE KILLED
LILLY KANE BECAUSE,

00:38.130 --> 00:41.133
AT THE TIME OF THE MURDER,
HE WAS IN THE COMPANY OF MISS...

00:41.140 --> 00:42.801
CHEYENNE.

00:42.810 --> 00:44.038
CHEYENNE.

00:44.040 --> 00:45.564
DEBORAH COLLINS,
YES.

00:45.570 --> 00:47.606
[ SIGHS ] KEITH, EVEN IF I DID
BELIEVE YOUR STORY --

00:47.610 --> 00:49.316
WHICH, AT THE MOMENT,
I DONT --

00:49.320 --> 00:52.471
THERES NO WAY TOP BRASS
WOULD RISK A STORY LIKE THIS.

00:52.480 --> 00:55.176
IF IT TURNED OUT TO NOT BE TRUE,
WE BECOME A NATIONAL JOKE.

00:55.180 --> 00:57.068
WELL, WE TRIED.

00:57.080 --> 00:58.479
IT IS TRUE.

01:00.330 --> 01:02.753
IM SERVING UP THE STORY
OF YOUR LIFETIME, LLOYD.

01:02.760 --> 01:06.082
LOOK, KEITH,
I CANT RISK MY CAREER

01:06.090 --> 01:09.093
BECAUSE OF TESTIMONY -- WITH ALL
DUE RESPECT -- OF A HOOKER.

01:09.100 --> 01:12.331
WELL, THERES MORE --
A LOT MORE. YOU READ IT.

01:12.340 --> 01:15.594
IF YOU THINK THERES MERIT,
TALK TO MISS COLLINS HERE.

01:16.640 --> 01:18.267
THAN KS.

01:20.750 --> 01:22.638
[ SIGHS ]

01:29.760 --> 01:32.649
[ LAUGHING IN DISTANCE ]

01:40.630 --> 01:41.767
HI, DAD.

01:41.770 --> 01:43.089
[ LAUGHING ]

01:43.100 --> 01:44.419
THIS IS SO STUPID.

01:44.430 --> 01:47.126
IM TELLING YOU --
NO TEARS.

01:47.130 --> 01:51.339
KEITH, THE RADIO --
LIKE OLD TIMES.

01:51.340 --> 01:53.137
IT WORKS, SEE?

01:53.140 --> 01:55.608
[ CONNIE FRANCIS
"WHERE THE BOYS ARE" PLAYS ]

01:55.610 --> 01:58.204
KEITH, TACOS.

02:00.790 --> 02:01.779
WHAT?

02:01.790 --> 02:03.348
ITS FUNNY TO ME

02:03.350 --> 02:05.648
HOW YOU ALWAYS HAVE YOUR MUSIC
MATCH YOUR MEAL.

02:05.650 --> 02:07.789
IT IS CALLED
"SE'I'I'ING A MOOD."

02:07.790 --> 02:09.894
OF COURSE.

02:09.900 --> 02:11.822
CONNIE FRANCIS
IS SPAGHE'ITI BOLOGNESE

02:11.830 --> 02:15.197
WITH CRUSTY BREAD
AND A NICE CHIANTI.

02:15.200 --> 02:17.896
UM, SANS THE CHIANTI.
[ CLEARS THROAT ]

02:19.240 --> 02:23.165
OKAY. SAY WE WERE HAVING
HOT DOGS AND TATER TOTS.

02:23.170 --> 02:25.661
LATE 70$ SOUTHERN ROCK --
SKYNYRD, MAYBE CREEDENCE.

02:25.670 --> 02:27.661
PORK CHOPS.
COUNTRY -- OLD SCHOOL.

02:27.670 --> 02:31.140
UNLESS ITS FRIED. THEN
ITS ELVIS, THE EARLY YEARS.

02:31.150 --> 02:32.447
[ CHUCKLES ]

02:34.320 --> 02:36.572
[ LATIN MUSIC PLAYS ]

02:36.580 --> 02:38.673
THERE YOU GO.
HOWS THAT?

02:38.680 --> 02:40.921
PERFECT.

03:03.750 --> 03:05.900
[ DOOR OPENS, CLOSES ]

03:05.910 --> 03:08.572
TELL ME THIS IS A JOKE.

03:08.580 --> 03:10.855
YOU WANT TO SUE
THE KANE FAMILY?

03:10.860 --> 03:12.851
YES.

03:12.860 --> 03:17.285
PLEASE TELL ME THERES
ANOTHER KANE FAMILY IN TOWN.

03:17.290 --> 03:19.224
MAYBE, UH,
BORIS AND GILDA KANE?

03:19.230 --> 03:20.299
TH EYLL SETTLE.

03:20.300 --> 03:22.359
OH. THEY WILL.

03:22.370 --> 03:24.429
WELL, THATS GOOD TO HEAR.

03:24.430 --> 03:27.297
SEEMS LIKE YOU HAVE THIS
PRETI'Y WELL SEWN-UP.

03:27.300 --> 03:29.404
ANYTHING YOU NEED ME
TO HAVE NOTARIZED?

03:32.740 --> 03:34.708
THERES PHONE RECORDS,
MAN.

03:34.710 --> 03:37.907
AND HOW DO YOU -- HOW DO YOU
EXPLAIN THE SHOES, HUH?

03:37.910 --> 03:39.446
IT DOESNT MEAN JACK.

03:39.450 --> 03:41.918
YOU NEED TO CHILL OUT, BEAV --
RIGHT NOW.

03:41.920 --> 03:44.639
TO THE GRAVE, MAN --
THATS WHAT WE SAID.

03:47.350 --> 03:50.319
"SINCE HIS REMOVAL FROM OFFICE,
KEITH MARS, THE OUSTED SHERIFF,

03:50.330 --> 03:51.991
"HAS TIRELESSLY
AND SINGLE-HANDEDLY

03:52.000 --> 03:53.729
"CONTINUED
HIS OWN INVESTIGATION

03:53.730 --> 03:56.221
DESPITE BEING SHUNNED
BY THE COMMUNITY AT-LARGE."

03:56.230 --> 03:57.652
YOUD THINK
IT MIGHT BE GROSS

03:57.660 --> 03:59.969
TO READ A LOVE LETTER
TO YOUR DAD, BUT I ENJOY IT.

03:59.970 --> 04:01.506
IF I WAS HIM,

04:01.510 --> 04:03.535
ID BE "I TOLD YOU SO"ing
ALL OVER NEPTUNE.

04:07.940 --> 04:10.943
MY "BLONDE PULLING ME
INTO THE GIRLS ROOM" FANTASY --

04:10.950 --> 04:12.269
RUINED!

04:12.280 --> 04:14.578
DO ME A FAVOR.
DO ME A FAVOR.

04:14.580 --> 04:16.810
GO OUTSIDE AND TELL ME
WHEN LOGANS GONE.

04:16.820 --> 04:18.412
OKAY.

04:18.420 --> 04:20.650
HOW MUCH LONGER
DO YOU THINK YOU CAN AVOID HIM?

04:24.390 --> 04:28.019
BELIEVE ME, THE LAST THING
I WANT TO DO IS HURT YOU.

04:31.970 --> 04:34.939
IF THERES A CHANCE
TO KEEP MY FAMILY TOGETHER,

04:34.940 --> 04:36.396
I HAVE TO TAKE IT.

04:36.400 --> 04:38.937
AND I...

04:38.940 --> 04:43.570
I JUST DONT KNOW...
WHAT ELSE TO SAY.

04:46.810 --> 04:48.539
YOURE REALLY DOING THIS.

04:48.550 --> 04:51.053
IS IT REALLY
WHAT YOU WANT?

04:51.060 --> 04:53.915
[ SIGHS ]

05:10.080 --> 05:11.707
EVERYTHING OKAY?

05:11.710 --> 05:13.507
OH, ITS FINE.

05:13.510 --> 05:17.378
I JUST HAD TO TELL ALICIA
THAT MY SITUATION HAS CHANGED.

05:18.980 --> 05:21.949
SORRY. I KNOW HOW MUCH
YOU CARE ABOUT HER.

05:21.950 --> 05:23.611
YEAH.

05:23.620 --> 05:26.589
SHES GOT TO UNDERSTAND,
THOUGH -- WITH MOM COMING BACK.

05:36.860 --> 05:40.102
DONT SEAT ENTERTAINMENT PEOPLE
NEXT TO THE CORPORATE PEOPLE.

05:40.110 --> 05:41.839
LETS KEEP IT CIVIL.

05:41.840 --> 05:44.900
JAKE, HONEY,
WHEN DID WE BECOME REPUBLICANS?

05:44.910 --> 05:46.332
WELL, WE HAVENT.

05:46.340 --> 05:48.467
WERE, UH...
WERE GOING WITH THE FLOW.

05:48.470 --> 05:52.770
BESIDES, THE GOVERNORS
VERY POPULAR, AND, HONESTLY,

05:52.780 --> 05:54.748
ITS GONNA BE GOOD
FOR BUSINESS.

05:54.750 --> 05:57.014
AND HIS SOCIAL POLICYS --
NO, JUST SPARE ME.

05:57.020 --> 05:59.113
SO, ANYONE
READ THE PAPER TODAY?

05:59.120 --> 06:01.623
GARFIELD -- I MEAN,
WILL HE EVER LEARN?

06:01.630 --> 06:04.884
THIS OTHER THING -- I GUESS
ABEL KOONTZ DIDNT KILL LILLY.

06:04.890 --> 06:06.949
LETS OPEN THE FLOOR
FOR DISCUSSION.

06:06.960 --> 06:09.463
ITS HOGWASH, DUNCAN --
AN INVENTION OF KEITH MARS.

06:09.470 --> 06:11.461
THE WOMAN WAS A PROSTITUTE,
FOR GODS SAKE.

06:11.470 --> 06:13.495
STOP! QUIT LYING TO ME!
DUNCAN, PLEASE.

06:13.500 --> 06:15.593
I CANT TAKE IT ANYMORE --
ALL THE LIES.

06:15.600 --> 06:18.660
DOES ANYONE EVER TELL ME
THE TRUTH, EVER?!

06:18.670 --> 06:21.377
YOU TREAT ME LIKE IM 6.
YOU ALWAYS HAVE!

06:21.380 --> 06:24.406
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW,
DUNCAN?

06:24.410 --> 06:26.048
DO YOU WANT
TO KNOW EVERYTHING?

06:26.050 --> 06:27.506
JAKE, NO!

06:27.510 --> 06:30.411
YEAH.
I WANT TO KNOW.

06:32.990 --> 06:35.015
YOU DID IT, SON.

06:35.020 --> 06:37.557
YOU HAD A FIT.
YOU KILLED YOUR SISTER.

06:40.000 --> 06:41.524
DUNCAN!

06:41.530 --> 06:43.395
DUNCAN, COME INSIDE.

06:45.170 --> 06:46.159
DUNCAN!

06:51.440 --> 06:52.475
DUNCAN!

06:52.480 --> 06:55.108
AAH!
[ SOBBING ]

06:56.010 --> 06:57.079
LILLY?

07:00.450 --> 07:02.042
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

07:04.050 --> 07:05.187
LOOK...

07:05.190 --> 07:07.545
IT WAS AN ACCIDENT,
DUNCAN.

07:07.550 --> 07:09.086
WE KNOW IT WAS.

07:09.090 --> 07:11.593
YOU DIDNT KNOW
WHAT YOU WERE DOING.

07:11.600 --> 07:13.192
YOU LOVED YOUR SISTER.

07:14.430 --> 07:17.922
WEVE DONE THIS
FOR YOU, SON...

07:17.930 --> 07:19.602
SO YOU COULD HAVE
A FUTURE.

07:19.610 --> 07:22.738
KEITH MARS IS SUING US.

07:22.740 --> 07:24.537
WEVE BEEN SERVED.

07:24.540 --> 07:26.565
[ SOBBING ]

07:32.550 --> 07:34.973
HELLO?

07:34.980 --> 07:36.015
BEAVER.

07:36.020 --> 07:38.875
ITS CASSIDY.

07:38.880 --> 07:40.586
MY REAL NAMES CASSIDY.

07:42.890 --> 07:45.029
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU,
CASSIDY?

07:45.030 --> 07:47.988
WELL, THERES SOMETHING
THAT YOU SHOULD KNOW.

07:47.990 --> 07:49.491
SPILL.

07:49.500 --> 07:50.967
THE WEEKEND
LILLY WAS KILLED,

07:50.970 --> 07:53.461
ME, DICK, AND LOGAN
WERE DOWN IN MEXICO SURFING.

07:53.470 --> 07:54.698
I KNOW THIS.

07:54.700 --> 07:56.736
YEAH, WELL, LOGAN,
HE, UH...

07:56.740 --> 07:58.537
HE GOT ALL WORKED UP --

07:58.540 --> 08:01.771
TALKING ABOUT HOW HE KNEW
LILLY WAS SEEING SOMEBODY NEW.

08:01.780 --> 08:03.247
YEAH?

08:03.250 --> 08:05.673
SO HE GOT UP EARLY
THAT MORNING --

08:05.680 --> 08:07.705
THE DAY
THAT LILLY WAS MURDERED.

08:07.710 --> 08:10.656
HE DROVE BACK TO NEPTUNE
TO SEE HER.

08:19.600 --> 08:22.819
BEAVER SAID THAT LOGAN
HAD BOUGHT LILLY A SHOT GLASS

08:22.830 --> 08:25.594
THAT HE FOUND IN A TOURIST SHOP
DOWN THERE.

08:25.600 --> 08:27.158
DOES THAT SEEM ODD TO YOU?

08:27.170 --> 08:30.606
NOT THAT ODD.
LILLY COLLECTED SHOT GLASSES.

08:30.610 --> 08:34.273
BEAVER SAID IT SAID
"I GOT BAKED IN ENSENADA."

08:34.280 --> 08:36.874
SHE WOULD HAVE LOVED IT.

08:36.880 --> 08:39.075
ARE YOU ALL RIGHT,
HONEY?

08:39.080 --> 08:41.287
YEAH.

08:41.290 --> 08:43.815
JUST. . .LOGAN.

08:43.820 --> 08:45.640
"BAKED IN ENSENADA"?

08:45.650 --> 08:46.912
VERONICA!

08:49.730 --> 08:51.254
WHAT ARE YOU
LOOKING FOR?

08:51.260 --> 08:53.057
THIS.
ITS AN INVENTORY --

08:53.060 --> 08:56.257
EVERYTHING IN LILLYS BEDROOM,
EVERYTHING IN LILLYS CAR.

08:58.160 --> 09:01.607
SHOT GLASS --
"BAKED IN ENSENADA."

09:01.610 --> 09:04.534
ITS HERE.
IT WAS IN HER CAR.

09:04.540 --> 09:07.008
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT THIS MEANS?

09:07.010 --> 09:10.013
IT MEANS
LOGAN FOUND LILLY.

09:10.020 --> 09:13.911
COME ON, BABY,
BE MY BAD BOYFRIEND

09:17.820 --> 09:22.052
GOT SOMETHING SPECIAL
FOR MY BAD BOYFRIEND

09:22.060 --> 09:24.585
HEY.

09:26.690 --> 09:28.681
OH. I EXIST?

09:28.690 --> 09:30.738
I THOUGHT
I FELT DIFFERENT TODAY.

09:30.740 --> 09:32.560
IVE BEEN AVOIDING YOU.

09:32.570 --> 09:35.960
[ SIGHS ] REALLY?
I HADNT NOTICED.

09:35.970 --> 09:37.835
IM SORRY.
I FREAKED OUT.

09:37.840 --> 09:39.899
THAT NIGHT
IN THE GUEST HOUSE,

09:39.910 --> 09:43.038
WE WERE, LIKE, CROSSING OVER
INTO SOMETHING, AND...

09:43.050 --> 09:46.247
ALL OF A SUDDEN, I JUST FELT
REALLY WEIRD AND GUILTY,

09:46.250 --> 09:48.639
AND I STARTED THINKING
ABOUT DUNCAN

09:48.650 --> 09:50.709
AND ABOUT LILLY, AND...

09:50.720 --> 09:53.655
IT WASNT THE EASIEST NIGHT
TO BEGIN WITH.

09:54.860 --> 09:55.849
I KNOW.

09:55.860 --> 09:58.078
I JUST COULDNT DEAL.

09:58.090 --> 10:00.024
WELL,
YOU COULD HAVE TOLD ME.

10:00.030 --> 10:02.590
EVEN IF YOU JUST SAID
"I CANT DEAL"...

10:02.600 --> 10:06.366
BUT YOU BOLT AND DODGE ME
FOR A COUPLE DAYS.

10:06.370 --> 10:08.019
ITS WHAT I DO.

10:08.030 --> 10:10.908
WHEN THINGS GET OUT OF CONTROL,
I NEED TO BE ALONE.

10:10.910 --> 10:13.276
LISTEN, YOU KNOW,
I AM FREAKED OUT, TOO.

10:13.280 --> 10:15.874
YOU KNOW,
THIS WHOLE ABEL KOONTZ THING...

10:15.880 --> 10:18.098
AND KNOWING WHAT WE DO
ABOUT DUNCAN.

10:18.110 --> 10:20.908
I DONT WANT TO BELIEVE
IT COULD HAVE BEEN HIM, BUT...

10:20.920 --> 10:23.241
ITS THE ONLY THING
THAT MAKES SENSE, RIGHT?

10:23.250 --> 10:25.286
I DONT KNOW.

10:25.290 --> 10:28.987
I HAVE THIS FEELING THAT THINGS
ARE GONNA GET REALLY BAD.

10:28.990 --> 10:30.696
YEAH?

10:33.760 --> 10:35.648
DONT RUN OUT ON ME AGAIN,
OKAY?

10:35.660 --> 10:38.299
IF YOU NEED TO DO WHATEVER,
YOU JUST LET ME KNOW.

10:38.300 --> 10:40.131
I NEED TO DO WHATEVER.

10:40.140 --> 10:43.667
JUST FOR A COUPLE OF DAYS.
THEN ILL BE BACK TO NORMAL.

10:43.670 --> 10:47.868
OR AS CLOSE TO NORMAL
AS I CAN GET.

10:47.870 --> 10:49.167
OKAY.

10:54.650 --> 10:55.947
YOU KNOW WHERE TO FIND ME.

10:58.280 --> 10:59.759
[ LOCKER DOOR SHUTS ]

10:59.760 --> 11:01.057
[ SPEED-DIALING ]

11:03.290 --> 11:06.157
ITS ME.
I JUST RAN INTO LOGAN.

11:06.160 --> 11:09.220
I KNOW, I KNOW.
I COULDNT HELP IT.

11:09.230 --> 11:12.165
HES TRYING
TO PIN IT ON DUNCAN.

11:12.170 --> 11:13.967
ANY NEWS ON TIJUANA?

11:13.970 --> 11:16.359
THE BORDER PATROL
GOT BACK TO ME.

11:16.370 --> 11:19.362
LOGANS CAR CROSSED THE BORDER
AT 8:57 AM.

11:19.370 --> 11:21.372
ON THE DAY
LILLY WAS MURDERED.

11:21.380 --> 11:23.348
BEAVER WAS TELLING
THE TRUTH.

11:23.350 --> 11:26.205
HE HAD PLENTY OF TIME TO GET
BACK TO NEPTUNE AND KILL HER.

11:26.210 --> 11:27.973
Okay, III see you later.

11:27.980 --> 11:29.345
HEY, ARE YOU OKAY?

11:29.350 --> 11:30.681
NO, IM FINE.

11:30.690 --> 11:32.885
I love you.
LOVE YOU, TOO.

11:32.890 --> 11:34.380
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

11:38.160 --> 11:40.367
THATS NOT
WHAT IT SOUNDED LIKE.

11:40.370 --> 11:43.396
HMM. IT SOUNDED A LOT LIKE
LOGAN KILLED LILLY.

11:43.400 --> 11:46.995
THESE RICH BOYS THINK
THEY CAN GET AWAY WITH ANYTHING,

11:47.000 --> 11:48.194
DONT THEY?

11:52.110 --> 11:54.374
MISS MARS MAY HAVE AGREED
TO HELP FIND YOUR SON,

11:54.380 --> 11:57.269
BUT IT WAS MR. MARS,
A LICENSED PRIVATE INVESTIGATOR,

11:57.280 --> 11:59.373
WHO LOCATED HIM
AND ENSURED HIS SAFE RETURN.

11:59.380 --> 12:01.848
ID BE HAPPY TO GIVE MR. MARS
A CHECK RIGHT NOW.

12:01.850 --> 12:03.340
Keith:
AND THE CONDITION?

12:03.350 --> 12:06.217
VERONICA RELINQUISHES ANY FUTURE
CLAIM TO THE KANE ESTATE.

12:06.220 --> 12:07.778
THE CONTRACTS ARE PREPARED.

12:07.790 --> 12:09.143
ALL WE NEED
IS YOUR DAUGHTERS SIGNATURE.

12:09.150 --> 12:10.924
FUTURE CLAIMS?
SO, WHAT?

12:10.930 --> 12:13.398
SHE SLIPS AND FALLS OUTSIDE KANE
ENTERPRISES -- TOUGH TOENAILS?

12:13.400 --> 12:15.994
I GUESS NOW IS A GOOD TIME
TO PROTECT YOUR ASSETS

12:16.000 --> 12:18.150
WITH THE ABEL KOONTZ WITNESS
COMING FORWARD.

12:18.160 --> 12:21.129
IM SURE YOULL ENCOURAGE YOUR
DAUGHTER TO DO THE RIGHT THING.

12:21.140 --> 12:22.903
IM WILLING
TO MAKE THIS DEAL,

12:22.910 --> 12:25.731
BUT ILL LET VERONICA
MAKE THE DECISION...

12:25.740 --> 12:28.402
ONCE I FIGURE OUT
HOW TO EXPLAIN IT TO HER.

12:28.410 --> 12:30.275
KEITH, WE BOTH KNOW
YOUR DAUGHTER KNOWS

12:30.280 --> 12:32.271
EXACTLY WHY SHES BEING ASKED
TO SIGN THIS.

12:32.280 --> 12:34.771
AND WE BOTH KNOW ITS BETTER
FOR EVERYONE IF SHE DOES.

12:41.830 --> 12:44.048
YOURE NOT TRYING TO BURN A HOLE
THROUGH A STACK OF PAPER

12:44.060 --> 12:46.426
USING ONLY THE POWER
OF YOUR STARE AGAIN?

12:47.930 --> 12:49.056
HEY, SWEETH EART.

12:50.470 --> 12:52.791
HAVE A SEAT A MINUTE.
I HAVE TO TALK TO YOU.

12:54.800 --> 12:56.836
I MET WITH CELESTE KANE
TODAY.

12:56.840 --> 13:00.241
SHES PAYING YOU DOUBLE AND
SPONSORING OUR CLUB MEMBERSHIP?

13:00.250 --> 13:02.548
SHE ACTUALLY
AGREED TO PAY UP, BUT...

13:02.550 --> 13:04.768
ONLY IF YOU SIGN
THIS CONTRACT

13:04.780 --> 13:07.408
THAT SAYS THAT
YOULL NEVER SUE THEM AGAIN.

13:07.410 --> 13:10.914
SHE WANTS YOU TO WAIVE ANY CLAIM
ON THE KANE FORTUNE.

13:21.430 --> 13:22.829
WHAT?

13:22.830 --> 13:24.798
WAS I SUPPOSED TO SIGN
IN BLOOD?

13:24.800 --> 13:27.166
YOU KNOW WHAT
YOU JUST SIGNED AWAY?

13:27.170 --> 13:30.230
THERES NOTHING
THAT I WANT FROM THEM.

13:30.240 --> 13:31.878
NOTHING?

13:32.940 --> 13:35.204
YOU DIDNT SIGN AWAY
A THING.

13:36.840 --> 13:40.048
VERONICA, I AM,
WITHOUT A DOUBT, YOUR FATHER.

13:54.960 --> 13:56.848
OHHHH!
YEAH, YOU ARE.

13:56.860 --> 13:59.829
DONT THINK THAT CHARM OF YOURS
IS LEARNED BEHAVIOR.

13:59.830 --> 14:01.263
THATS GENETICS, BABY!

14:03.510 --> 14:06.001
[ GASPS ]

14:06.010 --> 14:10.140
I SAY WE PUT A DENT IN THAT
FITY GRAND AND CELEBRATE.

14:10.150 --> 14:14.268
ACTUALLY, HONEY, THIS NEW
INFORMATION WE HAVE ON LOGAN --

14:14.280 --> 14:16.840
HIS ALIBI
IS COMPLETELY BLOWN.

14:16.850 --> 14:20.229
I THINK WE CAN FINALLY GO
TO THE AUTHORITIES.

14:23.390 --> 14:25.278
MM-HMM.

14:25.290 --> 14:27.349
[ DOORBELL RINGS ]

14:30.440 --> 14:31.896
AFTERNOON, SIR.

14:31.900 --> 14:33.265
SHERIFF. CAN I HELP YOU
WITH SOMETHING?

14:33.270 --> 14:35.966
YOU CAN SHOW ME
TO YOUR SONS ROOM.

14:35.970 --> 14:37.392
WERE GONNA NEED
TO SEARCH IT.

14:37.400 --> 14:38.992
WHAT DO YOU WANT
WITH MY SON?

14:39.000 --> 14:40.877
SOME NEW INFORMATION
HAS COME UP

14:40.880 --> 14:42.871
REGARDING
THE LILLY KANE MURDER CASE.

14:42.880 --> 14:45.303
WERE GONNA FOLLOW UP --
ROUTINE.

14:45.310 --> 14:47.574
WHOA, WHOA, WHOA.
YOU CANT JUST BARGE IN HERE --

14:47.580 --> 14:50.117
COME ON, NOW. YOUVE BEEN
IN WHAT -- 3O COP MOVIES?

14:50.120 --> 14:52.315
MAKE SURE YOU CHECK
THE AIR-CONDITIONING VENTS.

14:52.320 --> 14:53.981
GOTCHA, BOSS.

14:53.990 --> 14:56.015
OUR SNITCH SAYS THESE
CRAFTY LITTLE BUGGERS TODAY,

14:56.020 --> 14:57.487
THEY HIDE THINGS
IN THE VENTS.

14:57.490 --> 15:00.596
WAIT A MINUTE. WAIT A MINUTE.
WHERES MY SON?

15:13.680 --> 15:14.669
LOGAN ECHOLLS?

15:14.680 --> 15:16.272
YEAH.

15:16.280 --> 15:18.430
WHATS GOING ON?

15:18.440 --> 15:20.579
WED LIKE YOU TO COME WITH US
TO THE STATION.

15:20.590 --> 15:24.139
WE HAVE A FEW QUESTIONS
WED LIKE TO ASK YOU.

15:26.290 --> 15:30.056
YOU SAID YOU WERE IN MEXICO
THE DAY OF LILLYS MURDER. WHY?

15:30.060 --> 15:32.324
HOW MANY EPISODES OF "NYPD BLUE"
DID YOU HAVE TO WATCH

15:32.330 --> 15:34.059
TO GET
THE FINGER-TAPPING DOWN?

15:34.060 --> 15:35.357
I ASKED YOU A QUESTION.

15:35.360 --> 15:38.090
AND I IGNORED IT AND MOVED ON.
KEEP UP.

15:38.100 --> 15:40.637
DO I LOOK LIKE
I AM PLAYING AROUND WITH YOU?

15:40.640 --> 15:42.460
SO, HOW ABOUT
THAT PHONE CALL, HUH?

15:42.470 --> 15:43.698
OOPS.

15:43.710 --> 15:45.439
WHAT, YOU DIDNT READ
THE MANUAL?

15:48.040 --> 15:50.213
OKAY, I GET A PHONE CALL.
ITS THE LAW.

15:50.220 --> 15:52.347
YOUR DADDY IS ALREADY SENDING
YOUR LAWYER.

15:54.580 --> 15:55.615
GO AHEAD.

15:55.620 --> 15:57.508
[ SPEED-DIALING ]

15:57.520 --> 15:59.579
[ Ringing ]

15:59.580 --> 16:01.252
HEY, ITS ME.

16:01.260 --> 16:03.228
Hey, Im in
kind of a jam.

16:03.230 --> 16:06.586
Yeah, Im here at the lovely
sheriffs department.

16:06.590 --> 16:08.581
[ Chuckles ]

16:08.590 --> 16:11.036
BEING GRILLED WITHOUT
REPRESENTATION, I MIGHT ADD.

16:11.040 --> 16:13.235
DO YOU THINK
YOU COULD TRACK DOWN MY FATHER,

16:13.240 --> 16:15.231
MAYBE WORK
SOME OF THAT VERONICA MAGIC

16:15.240 --> 16:17.231
THAT GETS PEOPLE
OUT OF THESE THINGS?

16:17.240 --> 16:19.731
SURE. ILL DO
WHATEVER I CAN.

16:19.740 --> 16:22.004
THAN KS.

16:22.010 --> 16:24.149
ID LOVE TO CHAT,
BUT I HAVE A GUEST.

16:24.150 --> 16:25.674
[ CHUCKLES ]

16:25.680 --> 16:27.477
TALK TO YOU LATER.

16:27.480 --> 16:29.038
OKAY, BYE.

16:31.690 --> 16:34.557
[ SCOFFS ]
YOU CALLED UP VERONICA MARS?

16:34.560 --> 16:37.381
[ CLEARS THROAT ]
YEAH. WHATS IT TO YOU?

16:37.390 --> 16:40.666
ITS FUNNY, THATS ALL.
I JUST -- I MEAN...

16:40.670 --> 16:44.026
SHES THE ONE WHO CAME TO ME
WITH INFORMATION ABOUT YOU.

16:51.480 --> 16:52.378
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

16:52.380 --> 16:53.301
KEITH MARS, LINE TWO.

16:55.010 --> 16:56.568
KEITH,
WHAT CAN I DO FOR YOU?

16:56.580 --> 16:58.673
THE ECHOLLS KID,
WHATD YOU FIND OUT?

16:58.680 --> 17:00.284
AMONG OTHER THINGS,

17:00.290 --> 17:03.384
IM PRETTY SURE
HES DATING YOUR DAUGHTER.

17:03.390 --> 17:07.212
THAT GIRL OF YOURS,
SHES PRETTY HARD-BOILED, HUH?

17:07.220 --> 17:10.018
LOGAN --
WHERE IS HE NOW?

17:10.020 --> 17:12.557
WE LET HIM GO. WE DIDNT HAVE
MUCH TO HOLD HIM ON.

17:12.560 --> 17:13.754
HE LAWYERED UP.

17:13.760 --> 17:15.591
You know the deal.

17:15.600 --> 17:16.692
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

17:16.700 --> 17:19.555
LIANNE,
WHERES VERONICA?

17:19.560 --> 17:21.664
SHE TOOK BACKUP OUT.

17:25.140 --> 17:28.564
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

17:32.780 --> 17:35.248
SO, I GUESS
WE BROKE UP, HUH?

17:35.250 --> 17:37.468
WHAT DO YOU WANT ME
TO SAY, LOGAN?

17:37.480 --> 17:41.052
"LOGAN, IM GONNA GO HOME
AND PUT MY HEAD IN THE OVEN

17:41.060 --> 17:42.823
"BECAUSE I CANT GO ON
LIVING

17:42.830 --> 17:45.822
KNOWING WHAT A HEARTLESS BITCH
I AM!" -- SOMETHING LIKE THAT.

17:45.830 --> 17:48.458
SO, YOURE SAYING
YOU WAVES/IE DEAD?

17:48.460 --> 17:50.530
ONE WORD FROM ME,
AND BACKUP GOES FOR YOUR THROAT.

17:50.540 --> 17:52.292
[ SCOFFS ]

17:52.300 --> 17:54.791
IS THAT WHAT YOUD DO, BOY?
YOUD TEAR OUT MY THROAT?

17:57.200 --> 18:01.239
WHOS A MAN-KILLER, HUH?
[ LAUGHS ] WHOS A MAN-KILLER?

18:04.080 --> 18:07.470
YOU KNOW, I...
[ SIGHS ]

18:07.480 --> 18:09.368
I KNOW
LILLY WAS SEEING SOMEONE.

18:09.380 --> 18:11.587
IT WAS DRIVING ME CRAZY.

18:11.590 --> 18:13.581
WHEN I LEFT FOR NEPTUNE,
I DIDNT KNOW

18:13.590 --> 18:16.388
IF I WAS GONNA SCREAM AT HER
FOR TREATING ME LIKE DIRT

18:16.390 --> 18:17.687
OR BEG HER TO TAKE ME BACK.

18:17.690 --> 18:20.488
[ SNIFFLES ]

18:20.500 --> 18:22.627
AND I SAW HER
AT THE CAR WASH.

18:22.630 --> 18:24.393
I DIDNT SEE YOU THERE.

18:24.400 --> 18:26.459
WELL, I JUST PARKED ACROSS
THE STREET AND WATCHED HER.

18:26.470 --> 18:29.223
AND THIS FEELING CAME OVER ME,
YOU KNOW.

18:29.230 --> 18:33.200
I DONT KNOW HOW TO DESCRIBE IT,
BUT I JUST KNEW IT WAS OVER.

18:33.210 --> 18:37.499
SO, I SAT IN MY CAR, AND I WROTE
THIS NOTE TO HER, EXPLAINING IT.

18:37.510 --> 18:39.171
DID YOU GIVE IT TO HER?

18:39.180 --> 18:40.784
YEAH, I LEFT IT IN THE CAR.

18:40.790 --> 18:42.485
WITH THE SHOT GLASS.

18:43.790 --> 18:45.485
YEAH, WITH THE SHOT GLASS.

18:46.750 --> 18:50.197
IF YOU READ THAT LETTER,
YOUD KNOW ID NEVER HURT HER.

18:50.200 --> 18:52.350
[ HORN HONKING ]

18:53.800 --> 18:56.121
HEY! GET AWAY FROM HER!

18:56.130 --> 18:59.258
GET AWAY FROM HER NOW!

18:59.260 --> 19:02.502
BOY, I KEEP THINKING THAT THINGS
CANT GET WORSE, YOU KNOW.

19:02.510 --> 19:04.262
YOU KNOW WHAT?

19:04.270 --> 19:06.500
SHES ALL YOURS.

19:11.920 --> 19:13.876
YOU TWO ARE DATING?

19:13.880 --> 19:15.609
NOT ANYMORE.

19:19.250 --> 19:21.150
Veronica: DAD SAYS THAT,
THOUGH HIS DEPUTIES

19:21.160 --> 19:23.151
FOUND THE SHOT GLASS
LOGAN LEFT FOR LILLY,

19:23.160 --> 19:27.153
THE BREAK-UP LETTER LOGAN SAYS
HE WROTE WAS NEVER DISCOVERED.

19:28.690 --> 19:31.534
FRIENDSHIP NEVER ENDS

19:31.540 --> 19:33.428
IF YOU WANNA BE MY LOVER

19:33.440 --> 19:35.567
YOU HAVE GOT TO GIVE

19:35.570 --> 19:37.492
IF LILLY WANTED
TO KEEP IT A SECRET,

19:37.500 --> 19:39.639
I HAVE AN IDEA OF WHERE
SHE WOULD HAVE KEPT IT.

19:39.640 --> 19:42.905
Lilly: VERONICA,
YOU HAVE TO CHECK THIS OUT.

19:42.910 --> 19:45.401
THAT GUY I MET IN ITALY
LAST SUMMER...

19:45.410 --> 19:46.843
YEAH?

19:46.850 --> 19:50.172
HE SENT ME
SOME PICTURES.

19:50.180 --> 19:51.454
DOING SOME RE-WIRING?

19:52.590 --> 19:54.854
CELESTE IS A BIT
ON THE NOSY SIDE.

19:54.860 --> 19:56.384
YUCK.

19:56.390 --> 19:58.779
TELL ME ABOUT IT.
IM GETTING EVEN, THOUGH.

19:58.790 --> 20:00.667
I LEFT PHONE NUMBERS
ON MATCHBOOKS

20:00.670 --> 20:05.698
FOR TYRONE AND LEROY AND CHICO
AROUND THE ROOM --

20:05.700 --> 20:08.589
GIVE THE WOMAN A LITTLE DRAMA
IN HER LIFE.

20:08.600 --> 20:12.570
WAIT. WHOS TYRONE
AND LEROY AND CHICO?

20:12.580 --> 20:17.677
BEATS ME, BUT THEY SEEM
TO REALLY UPSET MOM.

20:17.680 --> 20:18.806
[ GASPS ]

20:18.810 --> 20:21.984
LILLY,
THOSE ARE NAKED PHOTOS.

20:21.990 --> 20:23.582
THEY CERTAINLY ARE.

20:23.590 --> 20:26.286
[ BOTH LAUGH ]

20:26.290 --> 20:28.212
IF LILLY KEPT LOGANS LETTER,

20:28.220 --> 20:30.529
THATS WHERE
SHE WOULD HAVE HIDDEN IT.

20:30.530 --> 20:33.556
NOW, WHAT DOES ONE WEAR
TO MEET THE GOVERNOR?

20:52.480 --> 20:55.938
HI, THE NUMBER TO THE
HAZELWOOD FACILITY IN SOQUEL.

20:57.920 --> 20:59.569
[ INDISTINCT CONVERSATIONS ]

20:59.580 --> 21:02.526
OF COURSE.
JUST TAKE IT OVER THERE.

21:02.530 --> 21:04.953
WELL TALK TO YOU LATER.
[ LAUGHS ]

21:16.740 --> 21:18.799
[ CRASH ]

21:51.840 --> 21:55.071
WHO THE HELL ARE YOU?
WHAT ARE YOU DOING IN HERE?

21:55.080 --> 21:56.707
DUNCAN!
DUNCAN, ITS ME!

21:56.710 --> 21:58.439
VERONICA,
WHAT ARE YOU DOING?

21:58.440 --> 22:00.419
IM LOOKING FOR SOMETHING.

22:00.420 --> 22:02.581
SHOULDNT YOU BE LOOKING
IN MY ROOM?

22:02.590 --> 22:04.842
THATS WHERE THE CLUES
WOULD BE, RIGHT?

22:04.850 --> 22:06.841
YOU DIDNT PUT ON
A WHOLE COSTUME

22:06.850 --> 22:08.886
AND SNEAK INTO MY HOUSE
JUST TO LEAVE EMPTY-HANDED.

22:08.890 --> 22:12.326
DUNCAN, STOP.
NO, COME ON. LETS SEE WHAT YOU
CAN FIND OUT. I WANT YOU TO.

22:12.330 --> 22:14.719
MAYBE I LEFT A CONFESSIONAL
ON MY ETCH A SKETCH!

22:14.730 --> 22:16.095
DUNCAN, CALM DOWN,
OKAY?

22:16.100 --> 22:19.627
I DONT THINK
YOU KILLED LILLY, DUNCAN.

22:21.110 --> 22:22.930
I THINK LOGAN DID.

22:25.010 --> 22:26.966
NO. NO WAY.

22:26.970 --> 22:29.438
HE WASNT IN MEXICO
THE DAY SHE WAS KILLED.

22:29.440 --> 22:31.476
DICK AND BEAVER
LIED FOR HIM.

22:31.480 --> 22:33.619
HE CAME BACK EARLY
BECAUSE HE FOUND OUT

22:33.620 --> 22:35.372
LILLY WAS SEEING SOMEONE --
WEEVIL, I THINK.

22:35.380 --> 22:36.847
AND HE ADMITTED THAT MUCH.

22:36.850 --> 22:38.841
BUT HE SAID HE WROTE HER
A LETTER ON THE DAY SHE DIED

22:38.850 --> 22:40.886
THAT WOULD PROVE
HIS INNOCENCE.

22:40.890 --> 22:44.382
I REMEMBERED LILLY USED TO HIDE
THINGS IN HER AIR VENTS.

22:48.790 --> 22:50.121
LETS SEE WHATS IN THERE.

22:54.870 --> 22:56.758
WELL?

22:56.770 --> 22:59.637
THERES JUST THESE.

23:02.110 --> 23:04.101
IVE GOT A CAMERA
WE CAN PLAY THEM ON.

23:18.420 --> 23:19.512
WHERES THIS?

23:19.520 --> 23:20.964
LOGANS.

23:20.970 --> 23:22.619
THE POOLHOUSE.

23:22.630 --> 23:24.029
[ SIGHS ]

23:24.030 --> 23:26.066
THATS
HER PEP-SQUAD OUTFIT.

23:26.070 --> 23:27.662
THIS...

23:27.670 --> 23:29.797
THIS IS THE DAY SHE DIED.

23:29.800 --> 23:33.634
COME HERE, LOVER.
TIME TO EARN YOUR KEEP.

23:47.690 --> 23:49.112
WHAT...

23:58.800 --> 24:00.904
LETS SEE THE OTHER TAPE.

24:04.970 --> 24:07.734
THIS ONES DATED
OCTOBER lst.

24:11.650 --> 24:13.845
[ MOANING PLEASURABLY ]

24:28.660 --> 24:30.491
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:30.500 --> 24:31.489
OH, MY GOD.

24:31.500 --> 24:32.660
MR. ECHOLLS?

24:37.900 --> 24:40.778
IVE GOT A SECRET --
A GOOD ONE.

24:50.050 --> 24:51.517
VERONICA?

24:53.590 --> 24:55.785
I KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

24:58.620 --> 25:00.053
I KNOW WHAT HAPPENED.

25:19.510 --> 25:22.115
OH, YOU DIRTY DOG.

25:28.750 --> 25:30.115
[ Singsong voice ] LILLY!

25:56.850 --> 25:58.317
I WANT THOSE TAPES BACK.

25:58.320 --> 26:01.721
MR. ECHOLLS, HI!
SORRY, LOGANS NOT HERE.

26:01.730 --> 26:03.721
I AM NOT PLAYING
WITH YOU.

26:03.730 --> 26:06.824
REALLY? YOURE USUALLY VERY
INTERESTED IN PLAYING WITH ME.

26:06.830 --> 26:08.149
GIVE ME THE TAPES NOW.

26:08.160 --> 26:10.549
LIKE YOU DONT SEE YOURSELF
ENOUGH ON FILM?

26:10.560 --> 26:12.835
I WANT THOSE TAPES,
YOU STUPID LITTLE BITCH!

26:12.840 --> 26:14.569
OH!
IM THE STUPID ONE?

26:14.570 --> 26:17.232
WELL, NOW YOU CAN JUST WATCH
THE TAPES ON "ACCESS HOLLYWOOD,"

26:17.240 --> 26:19.037
ALONG WITH
THE REST OF AMERICA.

26:53.010 --> 26:54.830
LILLY! LILLY!

26:55.810 --> 26:57.801
OH, MY GOD.
OH, MY GOD.

26:57.810 --> 26:59.175
LILLY, LILLY.

26:59.180 --> 27:00.738
LILLY, LILLY.

27:00.750 --> 27:02.980
LILLY, COME ON.
COME ON.

27:02.990 --> 27:04.912
LILLY, WAKE UP!

27:04.920 --> 27:08.219
[ Sobbing ]
LILLY...WAKE UP.

27:08.220 --> 27:10.950
WAKE UP.

27:10.960 --> 27:12.825
WAKE UP, WAKE UP.

27:12.830 --> 27:15.822
LILLY, WAKE UP.

27:20.360 --> 27:22.260
DUNCAN!

27:22.270 --> 27:23.339
AAAAH!

27:23.340 --> 27:25.035
DUNCAN,
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?!

27:25.040 --> 27:26.337
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE
TO LILLY?

27:26.340 --> 27:28.137
LILLY, HONEY, BABY.

27:28.140 --> 27:29.664
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE?!

27:29.670 --> 27:32.309
WHAT DID YOU DO, DUNCAN?!
WHAT DID YOU DO?!

27:32.320 --> 27:33.912
HONEY, HONEY...

27:35.950 --> 27:37.975
COULD HE REALLY DO IT?

27:37.980 --> 27:39.413
HES PSYCHOTIC.

27:39.420 --> 27:41.729
I WATCHED HIM BEAT A GUY
INTO A BLOODY MESS

27:41.730 --> 27:44.756
AND THEN ASK LOGAN
HOW HIS SCHOOLDAY WAS.

27:44.760 --> 27:46.387
HE BEATS LOGAN, YOU KNOW?

27:49.330 --> 27:52.959
HES HERE -- NOW.
HE CAME TO MEET THE GOVERNOR.

27:54.040 --> 27:57.339
I HAVE TO GET THESE TAPES
TO MY DAD. WILL YOU HELP ME?

27:57.340 --> 28:00.229
WILL YOU KEEP AARON IN YOUR
SIGHT AT ALL TIMES UNTIL I CALL?

28:00.240 --> 28:01.776
YEAH, OF COURSE.

28:01.780 --> 28:03.702
HEY.

28:05.780 --> 28:07.372
BE CAREFUL, OKAY?

28:09.450 --> 28:11.884
MY DAD
HAD A PATERNITY TEST.

28:14.690 --> 28:16.453
IM NOT YOUR SISTER.

28:21.070 --> 28:22.958
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

28:22.970 --> 28:24.119
Keith: Hi, sweetheart.

28:24.130 --> 28:25.961
DAD, ITS AARON ECHOLLS.
HE DID IT.

28:25.970 --> 28:28.962
I have video of Lilly in his bed
on the day she died.

28:28.970 --> 28:30.096
WHERE ARE YOU?

28:30.100 --> 28:31.738
IM JUST LEAVING
THE KANES.

28:31.740 --> 28:33.230
STAY PUT.
ILL BE RIGHT THERE.

28:33.240 --> 28:35.276
NO, DAD, HES HERE.
HES TALKING TO THE GOVERNOR.

28:35.280 --> 28:38.078
DUNCANS GONNA KEEP AN EYE ON
HIM. ILL BE HOME IN 10 MINUTES.

28:38.080 --> 28:39.707
COME STRAIGHT HOME.
DONT STOP FOR ANYTHING.

28:39.710 --> 28:40.984
OKAY.

28:40.990 --> 28:43.117
[ DIALING ]

28:43.120 --> 28:45.008
[ Ringing ]

28:45.020 --> 28:48.387
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

28:48.390 --> 28:50.415
IVE GOT A FEVER

28:50.420 --> 28:52.854
COME CHECK IT AND SEE

28:52.860 --> 28:56.990
THERES SOMETHING BURNING
AND ROLLING IN ME

28:57.000 --> 28:58.456
YOUVE REACHED LOGAN,

28:58.460 --> 29:00.121
AND HERE IS TODAYS
INSPIRATIONAL MESSAGE --

29:00.130 --> 29:02.030
ADVERSITY IS THE DIAMOND DUST

29:02.040 --> 29:04.838
WITH WHICH HEAVEN
POLISHES ITS JEWELS.

29:12.750 --> 29:16.470
I WANNA HEAR YOU
CALL OUT MY NAME

29:16.480 --> 29:19.972
I WANNA SEE YOU
BURN UP IN FLAMES

29:21.190 --> 29:25.183
SERIOUSLY, WHAT DO YOU...THINK
YOU CAN DO TO ME, HUH?

29:25.190 --> 29:27.454
ILL THINK OF SOMETHING.

29:27.460 --> 29:31.863
OH, COME ON, BABY,
BE MY BAD BOYFRIEND

29:34.340 --> 29:36.934
[ CELLPHONE RINGS ]

29:36.940 --> 29:38.237
HEY.

29:38.240 --> 29:39.798
I CANT FIND HIM.

29:39.800 --> 29:41.802
DID YOU ASK AROUND?

29:41.810 --> 29:44.199
IVE BEEN ASKING EVERYONE,
BUT NO ONE KNOWS WHERE HE IS.

29:44.210 --> 29:47.373
THANKS. WELL,
CALL ME IF YOU FIND HIM.

29:47.380 --> 29:49.200
LET ME KNOW
WHEN YOU GET HOME, OKAY?

29:49.210 --> 29:50.199
Okay.

29:50.210 --> 29:51.211
BYE.

29:51.220 --> 29:53.085
[ CELLPHONE BEEPS ]

29:53.090 --> 29:56.116
[ SIGHS ]

30:01.500 --> 30:02.967
AAAAAAH!

30:04.370 --> 30:05.928
KEEP DRIVING.

30:07.270 --> 30:08.897
UNH-UNH-UNH-UNH-UNH.

30:08.900 --> 30:09.924
DRIVING.

30:12.180 --> 30:16.139
WELL.
IVE BEEN LOOKING FOR THESE.

30:21.120 --> 30:23.509
[ TIRES SCREECHING ]

30:25.250 --> 30:29.038
[ HORN BLARING ]

30:34.860 --> 30:37.124
[ CELLPHONE RINGING ]

30:46.310 --> 30:49.507
Its Veronica.
Leave me a message.

30:49.510 --> 30:51.341
[ TELEPHONE BEEPS ]

30:51.350 --> 30:53.113
IS EVERYTHING OKAY,
KEITH?

30:53.120 --> 30:55.577
YEAH, EVERYTHINGS FINE.
ILL BE BACK SOON.

31:28.150 --> 31:29.139
[ COUGHS ]

31:29.150 --> 31:30.139
[ WHIMPERS ]

31:31.990 --> 31:33.514
[ MOANING ]

31:49.130 --> 31:50.324
HELLO?!

31:50.330 --> 31:51.570
HELLO?!

31:51.580 --> 31:52.899
[ KNOCK ON DOOR ]

31:52.910 --> 31:55.105
IS ANYONE HOME?

31:55.110 --> 31:57.408
HELP ME, PLEASE!

31:57.410 --> 31:58.570
HELLO?!

32:20.160 --> 32:24.039
HELLO?!
IS ANYONE HERE?!

32:32.320 --> 32:33.344
OHHHH!

32:39.180 --> 32:42.320
OHHHH! LET ME IN!
LET ME IN!

32:43.330 --> 32:45.457
PLEASE OPEN THE DOOR!

32:45.460 --> 32:48.088
PLEASE LET ME IN!

32:48.090 --> 32:50.126
PLEASE, PLEASE LET ME IN!

32:56.040 --> 32:59.237
[ WHIMPERING ]

33:01.580 --> 33:05.448
Aaron:
Veronica, youre an odd duck.

33:05.450 --> 33:09.341
How many teenage girls keep
walkieâ€”talkies in their car?

33:15.620 --> 33:17.417
WHAT HAVE YOU DONE TO ME?

33:17.420 --> 33:20.583
Veronica, dear,
where are my tapes?

33:22.230 --> 33:25.495
ILL LET YOU OUT AS SOON
AS I HAVE MY TAPES BACK.

33:25.500 --> 33:28.765
NO, THANKS.
HONESTLY, I FEEL SAFER IN HERE.

33:28.770 --> 33:32.001
WELL, YOU KNOW,
YOU SHOULDNT.

33:33.510 --> 33:34.499
[ SNIFFS ]

33:41.790 --> 33:44.782
YOU WANNA KNOW SOMETHING ABOUT
JOAN OF ARC, VERONICA? HUH?

33:44.790 --> 33:48.339
GOD DIDNT REALLY TALK TO HER.
HUH-UNH.

33:48.350 --> 33:51.649
Its _true.
I saw It on TV.

33:51.660 --> 33:55.096
YOU KNOW, IT WAS ONE OF THOSE
HISTORICAL FORENSICS PROGRAMS.

33:55.100 --> 33:57.751
THEY DECIDED THAT SHE HAD
A BRAIN TUMOR. HEH.

33:57.760 --> 33:59.751
BURNED ALIVE!

33:59.760 --> 34:01.307
WHAT A WASTE.

34:01.310 --> 34:03.403
SHE THOUGHT
HER DEATH MEANT SOMETHING...

34:03.410 --> 34:05.503
WHEN ALL IT MEANT
WAS SHE WAS CRAZY.

34:05.510 --> 34:07.239
THINK ABOUT THAT.

34:07.240 --> 34:09.401
VERONICA, WHERE ARE THE TAPES?

34:09.410 --> 34:11.674
Where are the tapes?!

34:19.780 --> 34:23.557
VERONICA.
WHERE ARE THE TAPES, VERONICA?

34:26.060 --> 34:27.322
WHERE ARE THE TAPES?!

34:27.330 --> 34:29.457
WHERE ARE THE TAPES?!

34:29.460 --> 34:31.234
YOU KNOW,
LILLY NEVER TOLD ME

34:31.240 --> 34:33.231
WHERE THE TAPES WERE HIDDEN,
EITHER.

34:33.240 --> 34:34.593
I-I kind of think

34:34.600 --> 34:38.195
theres a cautionary tale
in that, Veronica.

34:38.200 --> 34:39.792
SOMETHING LIKE...

34:39.800 --> 34:44.169
"IM NOT GONNA LET A 17-YEAR-OLD
PIECE OF ASS RUIN MY LIFE"!

34:44.180 --> 34:47.172
Theyre on the roof!
I put them on the roof!

34:47.180 --> 34:49.569
Please let me out.
[ Sobbing ]

34:59.860 --> 35:01.623
Keith: VERONICA!

35:01.630 --> 35:03.188
VERONICA!

35:03.200 --> 35:04.189
Dad?

35:09.300 --> 35:12.838
[ BOTH GROANING, STRAINING ]

35:55.780 --> 35:57.213
[ GASPS ]

36:12.670 --> 36:14.934
[ AARON COUGHS ]

36:21.680 --> 36:24.274
UNH-AAAH! AAAAAAAH!

36:24.280 --> 36:26.202
[ LAUGHING ]

36:27.680 --> 36:29.807
SHES IN THE FRIDGE,
KEITH.

36:29.810 --> 36:31.710
YOU MIGHT WANT
TO CHECK UP ON HER.

36:31.720 --> 36:34.712
AAAAAAAAAAAAAAAAA
AAA
H!
H!

36:38.790 --> 36:40.883
DA-A-A-A-A-A-A-D!

36:42.570 --> 36:43.559
DAD!

36:43.570 --> 36:45.720
HANG ON, HONEY!

36:53.580 --> 36:55.639
[ COUGHING ]

37:11.660 --> 37:13.389
[ COUGHING ]

37:17.300 --> 37:19.598
I LOVE YOU.
I LOVE YOU SO MUCH.

37:19.600 --> 37:21.636
I KNEW YOUD COME.
I KNEW YOUD SAVE ME.

37:26.640 --> 37:28.369
[ PANTING ]

37:45.730 --> 37:48.381
[ BACKUP GROWLS ]

37:51.370 --> 37:52.997
AAH!

37:59.900 --> 38:01.777
[ BARKING ]

38:04.380 --> 38:06.348
[ BARKING ]

38:14.760 --> 38:16.887
[ COUGHING ]

38:16.890 --> 38:20.451
IM SORRY, MAN. YOU WERE
IN THE MIDDLE OF THE STREET.

38:21.730 --> 38:23.698
OH, MY GOD.

38:23.700 --> 38:25.725
Y-YOURE AARON ECHOLLS.

38:27.400 --> 38:28.799
Help me.

38:28.800 --> 38:30.688
Veronica:
DONT TOUCH HIM.

38:30.700 --> 38:32.338
DO YOU HAVE A CELLPHONE?

38:32.340 --> 38:33.329
YEAH.

38:33.340 --> 38:34.830
CALL 9-1-1.

38:34.840 --> 38:37.809
WE NEED AN AMBULANCE, THE
POLICE, AND THE FIRE DEPARTMENT.

38:37.810 --> 38:40.506
[ INDISTINCT TALKING
ON POLICE RADIO ]

38:42.950 --> 38:46.909
YOU MEAN THE WORLD TO ME.
DO YOU UNDERSTAND THAT?

38:46.920 --> 38:48.649
ARE YOU LISTENING TO ME?

38:48.650 --> 38:51.528
HEY. WHOS YOUR DADDY?

38:51.530 --> 38:54.397
[ LAUGHS ] I HATE IT
WHEN YOU SAY THAT.

38:57.830 --> 39:01.459
AARON ECHOLLS, YOU HAVE
THE RIGHT TO REMAIN SILENT.

39:01.470 --> 39:03.108
ANYTHING YOU SAY WILL BE USED
AGAINST YOU IN A COURT OF LAW.

39:03.110 --> 39:04.862
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO AN ATTORNEY.

39:04.870 --> 39:07.703
IF YOU CANT AFFORD AN ATTORNEY,
ONE WILL BE APPOINTED TO YOU.

39:07.710 --> 39:09.337
DO YOU UNDERSTAND
THESE RIGHTS?

39:09.340 --> 39:10.739
YOU KILLED MY DAUGHTER.

39:10.740 --> 39:12.640
YOU KILLED MY DAUGHTER,
AND YOURE GONNA PAY FOR IT!

39:12.650 --> 39:14.117
I WANT YOU FRYING!

39:14.120 --> 39:17.578
ILL DESTROY YOUR FAMILY
AND EVERYONE YOU EVER LOVED!

39:17.580 --> 39:19.912
YOU KILLED MY DAUGHTER!
JAKE.

39:19.920 --> 39:21.854
YOU KILLED MY DAUGHTER!

39:21.860 --> 39:23.680
ILL WATCH YOU FRY,
AARON!

39:23.690 --> 39:26.955
Officer: YOU ARE UNDER ARREST
FOR OBSTRUCT ION OF JUSTICE.

39:26.960 --> 39:28.780
YOU HAVE THE RIGHT
TO REMAIN SILENT.

39:28.790 --> 39:31.463
MY DAUGHTE-E-E-E-R!

39:31.470 --> 39:33.597
MY DAUGHTE-E-E-E-R!

39:33.600 --> 39:35.864
MY DAUGHTE-E-E-E-R!

39:35.870 --> 39:38.361
MY DAUGHTE-E-E-E-R!

39:43.850 --> 39:46.774
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

39:52.890 --> 39:54.619
HELL BE FINE.

39:54.620 --> 39:55.757
WHEN?

39:55.760 --> 39:57.887
EVENTUALLY.
JUST BE PATIENT.

39:57.890 --> 40:00.484
AND YOU NEED
TO GET SOME REST.

40:00.490 --> 40:03.391
I WONT LET HIM WAKE UP
AND FIND HIMSELF ALONE.

40:03.400 --> 40:05.766
IS THERE ANYONE
THAT WE CAN CALL?

40:16.540 --> 40:17.905
HONEY?

40:19.740 --> 40:20.877
WHAT HAPPENED?

40:20.880 --> 40:22.939
ARE YOU OKAY?
WHERES YOUR FATHER?

40:22.950 --> 40:24.178
HES IN THE HOSPITAL.

40:24.190 --> 40:26.181
HES GONNA BE OKAY.

40:26.190 --> 40:27.919
VERONICA, WHAT HAPPENED?

40:27.920 --> 40:29.410
ITS OVER NOW.

40:29.420 --> 40:31.752
AND ILL TELL YOU
THE REST IN THE MORNING.

40:31.760 --> 40:33.796
BUT FIRST
I NEED YOU TO PACK.

40:33.800 --> 40:35.950
WHAT?
WHAT DO YOU MEAN?

40:35.960 --> 40:38.622
YOU CANT BE HERE
WHEN DAD COMES HOME.

40:38.630 --> 40:40.097
[ SCOFFS ] VERONICA.

40:40.100 --> 40:41.567
I KNOW, MOM.

40:41.570 --> 40:43.162
I KNOW YOURE NOT THROUGH
DRINKING.

40:43.170 --> 40:45.900
I KNOW YOU DIDNT
EVEN FINISH REHAB.

40:45.910 --> 40:47.707
YOU CHECKED YOURSELF OUT.

40:47.710 --> 40:49.928
AND THAT WAS
MY COLLEGE MONEY.

40:49.940 --> 40:52.943
I BET ON YOU, AND I LOST.

40:52.950 --> 40:55.077
IVE BEEN DOING THAT
MY WHOLE LIFE.

40:55.080 --> 40:57.844
AND IM THROUGH.

40:57.850 --> 40:59.044
VERONICA...

41:01.560 --> 41:03.824
ITS NOT EASY.

41:03.830 --> 41:06.082
I KNOW ITS NOT.

41:13.200 --> 41:16.135
[ MONITOR BEEPING ]

41:18.540 --> 41:20.030
HEY, YOU.

41:25.210 --> 41:27.747
VERONICA DIDNT WANT YOU
TO BE ALONE.

41:52.010 --> 42:01.840
LILLY, I HOPE YOULL
PICTURE ME IN YOUR DREAMS

42:01.850 --> 42:04.785
ISNT IT BETTER
LIKE THIS?

42:04.790 --> 42:06.883
SO MUCH BETTER.

42:09.790 --> 42:11.997
THIS IS HOW
ITS SUPPOSED TO BE.

42:12.000 --> 42:13.627
TOTALLY.

42:13.630 --> 42:18.658
THIS IS HOW ITS GONNA BE
FROM NOW ON.

42:18.660 --> 42:20.150
RIGHT?

42:20.160 --> 42:21.832
LILLY?

42:21.840 --> 42:24.308
[ SIGHS ]

42:24.310 --> 42:28.132
YOU KNOW HOW THINGS
ARE GONNA BE NOW, DONT YOU?

42:28.140 --> 42:29.903
YOU HAVE TO KNOW.

42:31.540 --> 42:33.713
JUST LIKE THIS.

42:33.720 --> 42:35.312
JUST LIKE THIS.

42:36.950 --> 42:40.317
DONT FORGET ABOUT ME,
VERONICA.

42:43.760 --> 42:46.627
[ SIGHS ]
I COULD NEVER.

42:46.630 --> 42:50.327
[ KNOCKING ON DOOR ]

42:52.770 --> 42:58.595
YOU USED TO PLAY

43:02.110 --> 43:04.999
I WAS HOPING
IT WOULD BE YOU.

